## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all perspectives on minority rights. Some sources may have inherent biases, and the lack of recent data could affect the comprehensiveness of the findings. Additionally, the focus was primarily on English-language sources, which may limit the global applicability of the conclusions. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, would provide a more nuanced understanding of the topic.